Definition: of or relating to the principles of totalitarianism according to which the state regulates every realm of life
Example: totalitarian theory and practice; operating in a totalistic fashion
Synonyms: noun, cognition, totalitarianism, totalistic, totalism, of, or, relating, to, the, principles, according, which, state, regulates, every, realm, life, theory, and, practice, operating, in, a, fashion
Category: adj.pert
